net.dean.jraw.models

Class LocationHint

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.models.LocationHint

  • public final class LocationHint
extends java.lang.Object
    Hints at where some data in a tree structure might be. The "top" of the tree is the root node, while the "bottom" is the deepest level in the tree. There will only be (at maximum) one instance of this class for every value in TraversalMethod. Instances of this class are immutable.
